br />\n<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16321372056c17ac89c0baf4cd0c94ada8e3e695","tid":818012,"uid":21699,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42722897e6934403a551bf3971bd36939096eb25","tid":818012,"uid":105678,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aba692b9ea20031d6ddeb2976eb5e0a517c62d37","tid":818012,"uid":75193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3e25365784082be4d9fd5fd7ab318d79fe58f61","tid":818012,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:44:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T21:24:01.000Z","msg":"audio delay唔係好感覺到？<br />\n可唔可以講解下<br />\n可能少睇片 播Spotify唔會知<br />\ninput delay我自己覺得好左好多 以前iOS 同android 差好遠 而家唔覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T22:59:19.000Z","msg":"用過iPhone 8，iTunes首次付款驗證問題如果唔記得咗，係冇辦法自己reset。<br />\n<br />\n打過去apple又要畀個驗證問題嘅答案佢。<br />\n<br />\n我就係唔記得個答案先打過嚟問有冇方法搞，哇屌你又要我畀個答案。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母打咗十鳩幾次都係同樣回應，閪到戇鳩。<br />\n<br />\n嬲嬲地轉會換咗部845嘅android，唔講邊部廢事畀人話打手。雖然冇話超越ios，但至少成部機係畀自己掌握，有咩問題上XDA搵個module fix翻，控制自如，唔使假借他人之手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講Andriod lag嘅呢啲100%係用開低階spec嘅android機，覺得Lag，又唔識做research，咪換部名氣大嘅apple機囉。<br />\n<br />\n以前啲垃圾機係會lag嘅，但自從835、845開始都仲話lag嘅，真係冇腦中嘅冇腦，科技盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIfans更喜歡不斷洗自己腦：<br />\n<br />\nuser unfriendly 都冇問題啦，煩啲係為我地安全著想，最緊要咩都唔使煩，apple會幫我地諗哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T23:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmo